The Telegraph - Calcutta : International

 Gandhi peer

 Moscow, June 4 (PTI): Russian President Vladimir Putin has described himself as a pure and absolute democrat whose only peer was Mahatma Gandhi.

 Of course I am a pure and absolute democrat, but the real problem is that after the death of Mahatma Gandhi, there is no one (for me) to talk to, Putin was quoted as saying by the Kommersant daily.




